{"tid":2329172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅鑼灣串謀暴動案 六男女案件表證成立 各被告須對控罪答辯","createTime":"2020-12-17T05:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T06:41:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c75c15739d8ac286d08cc75cb4cec0c2cb9b44dd","tid":2329172,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"警方去年10月1日在銅鑼灣一個單位搜出白電油、布條、防毒面具及玻璃樽等物品，事後拘捕一名電競手及另外5名男女，全控以串謀縱火罪。惟案件在區域法院開審當天，控方突改控各人串謀暴動罪，並將串謀參與非法集結列為交替控罪 。辯方早前指控方證據薄弱，申請各被告對控罪毋須答辯；惟法官沈小民今裁定案件表面證供成立，各被告須對控罪答辯。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，涉案單位位於銅鑼灣鵝頸橋旁的人和悅大廈，單位由第六被告透過Airbnb短期租用。警方去年10月1日突擊搜查單位，在其中一間房內發現正睡覺的首三名男被告，第四及第五女被告則在另一房中，五人正睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n警方搜屋檢獲五罐白電油、空啤酒樽、100條布條、黑衣、自製維園一帶地圖、對講機、15個打火機及防毒面具，單位內有數個背囊，背囊內有鎅刀、伸縮警棍、呼吸器及打火機等。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前於中段陳詞中指出，控方未能證明被告之間存在協議。其中被指租用涉案單位的第六被告，其大狀指租客名稱根本與被告名稱不相符，單位內也沒有任何屬於被告的物品。<br />\n<br />\n案件原訂今早 11時開庭，以宣佈裁定各被告面對的控罪是否表證成立；惟至11時20分，沈官著書記通知庭內人士，押後至12時半才開庭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/2YY6WC4MFBGIDCTEFI72EXQJQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F2YY6WC4MFBGIDCTEFI72EXQJQM%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=74db02a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F2YY6WC4MFBGIDCTEFI72EXQJQM%2F&h=c4052800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/2YY6WC4MFBGIDCTEFI72EXQJQM/</a>"},{"pid":"043dbd2520e51a71bc66a8e88b486950a6067409","tid":2329172,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"222df4549df9031f6a9cf685f5ff74998f5b6923","tid":2329172,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9176885e9e4d3d8507f8d9d67868e2963dd754f3","tid":2329172,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"所有被告決定唔作供"},{"pid":"8fc73a39b0f75b68b49dd9b51e1d640e0ebad641","tid":2329172,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fee69de88a8eadb54fa550d6e11fb8cd2aaff11","tid":2329172,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"對錯名嗰個都表證成立？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fba4da6219b904acf3737e24a14d55e3bab490a","tid":2329172,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5aba407092b3e8b29115f6192fde91b58c510d","tid":2329172,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92233ce02cf3000a45e286be4f2dff89debd909","tid":2329172,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5624657753cdc9909ea93d3b44d96a240cd0a1","tid":2329172,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12203&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=118fa22e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12203</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅六庭<br />\n#沈小民法官 #續審 (13/18)<br />\n<br />\nA1張,A2胡,A3陳,A4蘇,A5李,A6沈 (17-25)(#1001銅鑼灣 串謀參與暴動 交替控罪：串謀參與非法集結)<br />\n<br />\n案件簡要：6位被告被控於2019年9月28日至10月1日，與不知名人士串謀參與暴動 。6人亦被控於2019年9月28日至10月1日，在同年同月同日與不知名人士串謀參與非法集結。<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n沈官裁定所有被告表證成立。所有被吿不會作供，亦不會傳召辯方證人。<br />\n<br />\n案件會押後至2020年12月22日1430續審，屆時控辯雙方將進行有關書面陳詞的補充及回應。他們需於12月21日前向法庭呈上書面陳詞。"},{"pid":"c044dcdc59b96187ec521fdd1d689411cfa7ae8a","tid":2329172,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"表証成立同判刑都差好遠<br />\n<br />\n有晒材料控方點尻up都得，又好難唔成表証"},{"pid":"1ad263c7a49ec75f047d43ba3dd96e570a984662","tid":2329172,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"多謝晒各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />及到場支持既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9261581308c030d64bd02ce96165fcda2f492da4","tid":2329172,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fdebe6228ccd6fa9bb5e1c2d11c25e7ca98898","tid":2329172,"uid":130355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdf34c3ef79ee677fd0d91771f2a2cf0a0cfee4b","tid":2329172,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"沈小民都叫55波既"},{"pid":"c6bea365c1be812a5942c9a3e66e135f93df42ac","tid":2329172,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"一路屌控方但又畀佢玩嘢"},{"pid":"923312f3fd3aa9f40b77435579e8150544f94